data.description: Stunning home located in the highly desirable exclusive gated community of Stone Gate in Riverside's Mission Grove ! This cozy three bedroom home plus a den offers, beautiful vaulted ceilings, stainless steel appliances, quartz counter tops, upgraded cabinetry, solar, sparkling pool and spa perfect for entertaining family and friends! The kitchen opens to a dining area and family room overlooking the private backyard and pool. This highly upgraded home shows beautifully and feels like a model home! Enjoy the community amenities featuring tennis courts,basketball, volley ball and private park! This home is conveniently located to local shopping, movie theater, dining, fitness centers and more! You do not want to miss this opportunity to own this lovely home! Contact us today to schedule a private showing!
